creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml:
With the Side Quest Fitness App, you can start tracking your workouts and meals, measuring results, and achieving your fitness goals, all with the help of your personal trainer.

Download the app today. And be sure to check out our website at: sidequestfitness.trainerize.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Consistency is key with this release! Introducing habit streaks and achievement badges—a new way to motivate clients to build healthy habits! Clients can create habit winning streaks by completing a habit every day that it’s scheduled into their calendars. As their streak continues to grow, they'll unlock special achievement badges at various milestones. 

As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.

Now, clients can leave their phones behind and be able to start and track any workout (regular, circuit, and interval), including three new cardio activities, swimming, dancing, and HIIT, directly from their watch!
